---
// ProblemSection - The Gym Owner's Dilemma: 3 pain point cards
---

<section class="problem-section noise-bg">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>
        Not Enough People <span class="dim">Coming Through Your Doors</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="section-desc">
        You've got a great gym. The members you have love the place. But new faces aren't walking in consistently, and the ones that do inquire rarely show up. It's not your offer. It's that nobody's steering the growth.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="cards-grid">
      <div class="pain-card">
        <div class="icon-wrap icon-red">
          <iconify-icon icon="lucide:archive" class="card-icon"></iconify-icon>
        </div>
        <h3>A List You're Not Using</h3>
        <p>
          Hundreds of old leads and past members are sitting in your system right now. They already know your gym. Most owners never reach out, and it's easily the biggest pile of money you're leaving on the table.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="pain-card">
        <div class="icon-wrap icon-orange">
          <iconify-icon icon="lucide:target" class="card-icon"></iconify-icon>
        </div>
        <h3>Ads That Don't Pay Off</h3>
        <p>
          You've tried boosting posts or running ads yourself. Maybe you even hired an agency. The leads came in, but hardly any of them showed up. You're left wondering if ads just don't work for your gym.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="pain-card">
        <div class="icon-wrap icon-yellow">
          <iconify-icon icon="lucide:phone-missed" class="card-icon"></iconify-icon>
        </div>
        <h3>Nobody to Chase the Leads</h3>
        <p>
          Your front desk is running classes and helping members. By the time they get around to calling a new lead back, that person has already signed up somewhere else. The follow-up never happens, and it's killing your growth.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .problem-section {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: var(--page-bg);
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .problem-section { padding: 8rem 0; }
  }

  .container {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .container { padding: 0 2rem; }
  }

  .section-header {
    max-width: 48rem;
    margin: 0 auto 4rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display, 'Clash Grotesk', sans-serif);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .dim { color: var(--text-dim); }

  .section-desc {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .cards-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .cards-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
  }

  .pain-card {
    background: var(--surface2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 1rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    transition: border-color 0.3s;
  }

  .pain-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent-hover-border);
  }

  .icon-wrap {
    width: 3rem; height: 3rem;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .icon-red { background: var(--red-icon-bg); }
  .icon-red .card-icon { color: var(--red-icon-text); font-size: 1.5rem; }
  .icon-orange { background: var(--orange-icon-bg); }
  .icon-orange .card-icon { color: var(--orange-icon-text); font-size: 1.5rem; }
  .icon-yellow { background: var(--yellow-icon-bg); }
  .icon-yellow .card-icon { color: var(--yellow-icon-text); font-size: 1.5rem; }

  .pain-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display, 'Clash Grotesk', sans-serif);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .pain-card p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

</style>
